sequenceDiagram
    participant TV as TradingView
    participant Flask as Flask Server
    participant TA as TradingAgents
    participant Data as yfinance/AlphaVantage
    participant T212 as T212 API

    TV->>+Flask: 1. Webhook POST (alert)
    Flask->>+TA: 2. Call propagate()
    TA->>+Data: 3. Fetch market data
    Data-->>-TA: 4. Return OHLCV, fundamentals
    TA->>TA: 5. Run analysts
    TA->>TA: 6. Researchers debate
    TA-->>-Flask: 7. Return BUY/SELL/HOLD
    alt Signal != HOLD
        Flask->>+T212: 8. POST /v2/orders
        T212->>T212: 9. Execute order
        T212-->>-Flask: 10. Confirmation
    end
    Flask-->>-TV: Response